FT  06 SEP 94 / UK Company News: Advanced Media share placing
Advanced Media Group, the interactive multimedia company, has placed 400,000
ordinary shares, with warrants attached on a 1-for-5 basis, at 110p each.
The placing, which represents 33.9 per cent of the equity and values the
company at Pounds 1.3m, will fund the next stage of AMG's expansion into the
mainstream of multimedia development and publishing.
Dealings on the 4.2 market, formerly the 535(2) market, began yesterday.
